Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 劃過天際的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心貧瘠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.16,0:00:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理讓你輕鬆解壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.22,0:00:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件牽扯到演員的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光鮮亮麗的背後隱藏著嫉妒的殺意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光鮮亮麗的背後隱藏著嫉妒的殺意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.10,0:00:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.76,0:00:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.83,0:00:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.85,0:00:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.42,0:01:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞臺女演員殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是爸爸的師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸過去就是個糊裡糊塗的傻東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸過去就是個糊裡糊塗的傻東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.05,0:02:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是當刑警還是當了偵探以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.05,0:02:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是當刑警還是當了偵探以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是常常要我這個老師父幫他擦屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.07,0:02:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說老伯伯難道是鹽田平八郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱日本福爾摩斯的就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽田平八郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個老先生就是傳說中的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.19,0:02:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最近毛利好像挺活躍的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就過來看看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.35,0:02:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸今天剛好有點事出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說好像是有個著名的劇團受到威脅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.80,0:02:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 快點帶我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子可以看到傳說中的名偵探的推理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻停止公演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.43,0:02:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然的話 你們就會看到恐怖的慘劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.43,0:02:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然的話 你們就會看到恐怖的慘劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.93,0:02:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有線索啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子還沒有來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼時候開始排演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像還沒有那個心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.81,0:03:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.94,0:03:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是在電視上走紅 她就開始擺架子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.43,0:03:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然都認為那是惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.47,0:03:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家還是怕得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請您調查一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不要妨礙我們的演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.86,0:03:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個案子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹽田平八郎先生要我帶他來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個老頭子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.01,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到這裡以後馬上就不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.68,0:03:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.01,0:03:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父 你在這個地方幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才這個臭老頭突然摸我的屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都這把年紀了 活不了幾年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都這把年紀了 活不了幾年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個色老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 祥子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們每個人都在跟我作對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最離譜的就是這個爛導演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.19,0:04:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種演員什麼時候輪到他來指導我演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外要我和分手的男朋友搭檔算什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以為她是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說出現就出現 還來打擾我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女演員還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股就是人生的寶礦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.72,0:04:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要稍微摸一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能知道這個人的生活方式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是名偵探嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫做走位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫做走位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是這樣決定演出時的位置的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在燈光都打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.56,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我們也要把每個演員站的位置決定好才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.38,0:05:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到演戲這麼麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個外行人不要干涉行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是要干涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個星期排演的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.73,0:05:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個照明燈差一點就掉到祥子小姐身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.02,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是說 是我故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是說 是我故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來舞臺的上面是這個樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便妳怎麼調查都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子小姐被人家盯上了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.49,0:05:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.09,0:05:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能到這裡來 這裡很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.17,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手的目標是大出祥子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我真的要下地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不跟妳分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.31,0:06:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 我願意陪你到天涯海角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.32,0:06:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間的愛情將化作星辰 一同奔向天國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.24,0:06:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊 如果真的要死的話 還需要講這些廢話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的願意死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能夠跟你在一起 我什麼都不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.69,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爛的戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天的表演太有震撼力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也被妳剛才的演技給嚇到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.34,0:07:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子…妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子 妳太入戲了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人從現在開始都不准離開現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.62,0:07:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 竟然在我眼前殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的皮膚呈現粉紅色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體由內向外浮出的斑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.76,0:07:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是利用氰酸化合物進行的毒殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽田先生 你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽到你跟毛利的傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以特地到這裡來看看你們到底進步到什麼程度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.86,0:07:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是已經退休了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要妨礙我們辦案好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.38,0:07:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在倒是會說大話了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了 你還是菜鳥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那個連續殺人犯明目張膽地跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那個連續殺人犯明目張膽地跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看面臨被革職時是誰救了你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.82,0:08:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.99,0:08:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件無解的密室殺人案的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也是我幫你解開的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也是我幫你解開的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實兇手早就留下蛛絲馬跡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被鹽田先生搶先破案的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以後我的耳朵就有得受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.96,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我在這兒慢慢的見習好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.83,0:08:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在演戲的時候偷偷下藥殺人的宇田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是一派胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就沒有殺祥子的動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.89,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒未必吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不是跟祥子交往過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.02,0:08:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 最近祥子在電視上走紅之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你分手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.74,0:08:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不屑於祥子的演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎每次都會跟她發生爭執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.78,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人爭執都是為了讓整部戲更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你說得那麼好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你說得那麼好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝下氰酸化合物的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎都是立即死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子小姐演戲時把藥服下去之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不慌不忙地喝了一杯水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不慌不忙地喝了一杯水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表明她服下去的藥裡面沒有被下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你看清楚這裡面到底有沒有毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就證實給你看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手到底是如何讓祥子小姐服毒的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排演前曾有長達四十分鐘的休息時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算兇手在排演之前讓她服下膠囊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠囊溶化也需要十五分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且時間不容易掌握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用速效藥也是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.50,0:09:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以為她是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時把那杯白開水拿到舞臺上的就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時把那杯白開水拿到舞臺上的就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有長進嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那師父認為兇手是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是基本中的基本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.79,0:09:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那杯水送到舞臺上的就是一個女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.11,0:10:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話 那個女的拿來的水裡面有毒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.57,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 我沒有在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是看後臺太亂了 所以才要整理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到妳好像在藏什麼東西 拿給我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.71,0:10:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底認為我做了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過 在結束辦案前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都不能離開現場的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.75,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個便條紙和恐嚇信用的是同一種紙耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.41,0:10:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子 竟然又來妨礙我辦案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情哪有這麼容易就知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.59,0:10:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這上面還有用筆寫過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.90,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次真是多虧了爺爺 案子才能順利地解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是您怎麼會知道兇手是女的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前不是常說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切犯罪的後面都有一個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.32,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.65,0:11:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.44,0:11:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.52,0:11:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…最重要的氰酸化合物沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認那張恐嚇信是我寫的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我絕對沒有殺那個女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.58,0:11:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.45,0:11:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳自從主角被祥子搶走之後不是一直對她懷恨在心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你還不是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說要是那個女人死了的話就好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說要是那個女人死了的話就好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部戲要是流產的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最傷腦筋的就是我耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 都冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.66,0:11:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們檢驗了被害人玻璃杯裡面剩下的水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有氰酸的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是水壺裡面沒有任何異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人果然是妳殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我殺的 糊塗偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我殺的 糊塗偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.87,0:11:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在英子把玻璃杯端出去之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個盤子是從舞臺旁邊接過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 就是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個玻璃杯其實是館岡先生幫我準備好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把盤子交給她的是我沒錯 但是我可沒有下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我記得祥子曾經要我把你排除在名單之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有什麼恩怨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經紀人佐佐木瞳小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經紀人佐佐木瞳小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.57,0:12:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽說過什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說館岡先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經偷看過祥子小姐換衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 他是因此而懷恨在心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對不可能是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.09,0:12:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他不是女的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的真清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼基本中的基本啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本中的基本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.26,0:12:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,館岡先生如果是殺害祥子小姐的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在道理上根本就說不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.85,0:12:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個杯子是同一種款式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排演的時候究竟哪一杯會放到祥子小姐面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要完全取決於飾演女侍的英子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不可能會是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你快點招供吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣反而會痛快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的 我沒有在杯子裡面下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓她受點傷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才在簾幕上動了點手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.35,0:13:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在簾幕上動了手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下來
